description: If you encounter an S3 error even if your video-clip is of valid size and format, it is probably due to the handshake failure. So, in that case, uploading the file once again can resolve the problem.
title: What is S3 error? Why am I not being able to add video-clips?
description_text: If you encounter an S3 error even if your video-clip is of valid size and format, it is probably due to the handshake failure. So, in that case, uploading the file once again can resolve the problem.
